values: Panther Pride Night was last night and we performed and did awesome...or so people say..I was just happy that I didn't fall! : )  So school started..: (  blah!! lol but it was good seeing everyone again.. but it's gay having to wake up at 6:30!!! lol I'm so tired by like 9:00 and like I never go to bed that early so it's way weird...lol ok so yesterday I wake up and start doing homework when my mom comes upstairs and says there are some football guys here to see you...and I'm like eew...I have not yet brushed my hair, washed my face, or even freaking brushed my teeth so I'm really really gross..I'd been up for like maybe 15 minutes...so I'm all like tell them to go away lol and she's like no no they really want to see you and so I go downstairs ugly and all..and guess who it was...Ricky...lol oh joy! (can you sense the sarcasm??) lol but yea I was like gross don't' come see me early in the morning! lol but he's a nice guy...and then yesterday I did chores and homework...ok so I had the weirdest dream last night...that Jonathon and I were back together again and we had a fight...because apparently he had told me his dad was dying and I didn't like care...and the weirdest thing was he was still living here but his parents were in Wisconsin and then the fact that his dad was dying was really weird because he started crying and then I started crying...I don't know it was a really strange dream...there was more to it I just can't explain it to make sense...So my life is all right..pretty hectic...I have so much stuff going on like I don't even get a second to myself so I'm like ahh!! lol and yea I'm sorta dating Ricky and he's really nice but I don't know I feel like I barely talk to him and that's really weird to me cause when I date guys we usually talk all the time and stuff...maybe it's cause we're not going out and he's not used to that I don't know...but I think it'll be weird for us if we go out...because we don't have any of the same friends...except for like Keith and Daniella...I don't know I think it's going to be really hard/weird but we'll see what happens...lol well I'm gunna go shower and finish my homework!!

I am sooo weird! lol I don't know I'm the biggest baby and I can't make up my mind. I don't know what I want..and I'm fine with that. Wait no, I'm not but I don't know how I'm supposed to find out what I want. LIke I'm torn I want to change things and start over but I don't want to let go in fear of tearing away what I fell in love with. And I wonder what I fell in love with, I don't know if it was the whole situation or the actual thing, which is part of the reason I can't decide what I want. And I'm like well I'll just wait it out  for things to happen  but everyday I get more and more anxious to make my life. I'm one of those people that decides their life I can't leave it up to chance or fate even though I should or at least up to God. I don't know but I can't just sit back and hope for things to happen I have to change them. But it's like I don't know how I want to change them. And worst of all I don't want to hurt anyone or anything while I figure that out. So I don't know...and it's like some many things remind me of how I want things to be but I know I can't make them like that. So to sum it up...I know what I want but I can't have that and then I have to decide between the two things I can have and I don't know if I even want either of them. So in other words it's gay. lol But I mean at least I'm happy about how things are right now, sorta. But every once in a while I still feel like crying but I don't not because I hold it back but because I don't feel like there's anything to cry about, if that makes sense (there might be one tear though) lol. But I need to stretch and then go to bed cause once again I have early practice tomorrow : (  but it's fun I promise! lol Sweet dreams!

I like woke up so freaking early for no reason : (   and I woke up without a shirt on...lol I was really weirded out, but knowing how much of a weird sleeper I am, I probably took it off cause I got hot and can't remember...but it was weird. And then I went out to eat cause it was my daddy's birthday!! It was fun...but then I went to dance and it was soooooo freaking hot!!! but it was still fun! umm then I hung around all day and then Matt called and we went to see Signs again..it was a really good movie, if you haven't seen it go see it! lol and now I'm dead tired and I have to wake up at like 6:30 tomorrow so I guess I'll go...but what I was confused about...well I figure I'm not going to worry about it I'm just going to let things happen and not try to want things to happen a certain way...but I still wish things were back to normal. Sweet dreams!!

I AM SO FREAKING CONFUSED

I seriously don't know what I should know or what I think anymore..I thought I figured it out today, but obviously I didn't. I thought I knew how I wanted things to be but everything has flipped. I'm so confused and I wish I didn't even have to think about this. I thought I'd gotten over all this stuff and those feelings and maybe it's not that I <i>have<i> those feelings anymore but I miss them? I dunno I'm scared of hurting someone I care so much about but I'm more scared of hurting myself. And I shouldn't be  cause I've already hurt myself more than I needed to but maybe I'm just doing this to forget about it. I dunno I wish things were ordinary.

Trying to be so perfect"

wow I had an interesting day today...lol Dance was good I had fun...tiring and hot but fun...my toe still hurt likes a mother though  : (   but um yea my day was good then I went out with some friends, Keith and Ricky. They're always fun but they won't stop making fun of me! lol then again I'm an easy target...I'll have to admit..but they're fun we um went to return some of Ricky's shoes and then went to his house and watched white man can't jump...am I the only one that didn't really get into that movie? lol it was funny though..and yea we had fun. G'NIGHT!! Sweet Dreams...

I thought I was really forward about my feelings and that I didn't hide things. But obviously the more I tell myself I'm over it the more I realize I'm not and that I wish things were back to normal. It hurts to wish things back to how they were when I used to think I was so unhappy before when things were normal when the were actually lovely. The only thing that gets my mind off all those things is dance, while I'm at practice nothing else matters and I wish that's how things were all the time that I wouldn't think about everything and that everything would change as easily as you can change the music in dance. ah I'm rambling...whatever I just wish I could be honest about my feelings instead of hiding them and changing them so I can seem so much stronger then I really am. 

"I'm feeling nervous
Trying to be so perfect"

I hate that feeling that you get <regret...that's the feeling> I wish I could've changed a lot of stuff this year...or actually had made some different decisions...but I'm all right.
